@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}

<section class="cp-section cp-page-hero">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="page-title">About AI Insights</h1>
        <p class="page-subtitle">We turn complex data systems into simple, trustworthy conversations for every team.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="cp-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="glass-card p-4 h-100">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-3"><i class="bi bi-people-fill me-2 text-primary"></i>Who We Are</h2>
                    <p>We are a data engineering team passionate about making data accessible to everyone. Our background is in data engineering, data warehousing, and AI, and we built AI Insights to make enterprise data easier to use in everyday work.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="glass-card p-4 h-100">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-3"><i class="bi bi-bullseye me-2 text-primary"></i>Our Mission</h2>
                    <p>Our mission is to eliminate the gap between business users and data. We believe every person in an organization—not just data teams—should be able to ask questions and get instant, trustworthy answers without SQL, BI complexity, or IT tickets.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="glass-card p-4 h-100">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-3"><i class="bi bi-chat-square-text-fill me-2 text-primary"></i>What is AI Insights?</h2>
                    <p>AI Insights is a conversational analytics platform. It connects to your existing data sources, deploys AI agents that understand your business context, and returns answers in plain English with auto-generated charts and reports.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="glass-card p-4 h-100">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-3"><i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill me-2 text-primary"></i>The Problem We Solve</h2>
                    <p>Data is often trapped behind technical complexity. Business teams wait days for reports while data teams get overloaded with ad-hoc requests. AI Insights removes this bottleneck with self-serve, conversational analytics.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="glass-card p-4 h-100">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-3"><i class="bi bi-cpu-fill me-2 text-primary"></i>Our Technology</h2>
                    <p>Built on a modern cloud-native stack—ASP.NET Core 8, Cohere AI, and Chart.js—AI Insights is secure, scalable, and designed for enterprise teams that need speed and governance together.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="glass-card p-4 h-100">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-3"><i class="bi bi-stars me-2 text-primary"></i>Our Vision</h2>
                    <p>We’re expanding to 15+ data connectors, collaboration workflows, scheduled reports, and embedded analytics—all powered by conversational AI that keeps getting smarter with your business context.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
